            <title>[LU-46] test-framework does not pick module parameters</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-46</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A change was introduced into test-framevork load-module function that incorrectly assumes wrong format for /etc/modprobe.conf file and so the regexp used cannot ever match anything.&lt;br/&gt;
